data.description: Spacious, Private, and beautiful one-level ranch home situated on 10 acres which is bordered by National Forest.  Living room and Kitchen established in a modern hardwood floor plan style.  Master bedroom feels oversized with great lighting and larger walk-in closet.  Master bathroom provides two vanities and a spa bathtub.  Guestroom has walk-in closet and full size bathroom.  The third room is spacious with full size closest.  A washer/dryer room with access to the back deck. There is a front deck and back deck that leads to the pool deck area.  The 25ft above ground pool is enclosed by a wood railing that has surround sound speakers attached to it.  A carport for two vehicles and an enclosed grill area.  Additionally on the property are three additional car ports, a 8x12ft tool/storage shed, a 10x20ft office building, a fenced in garden area, and a all purpose 16x26ft building.
data.whatILove: This home is a surprise.  It is spacious, private, and provides everything that we needed to feel comfortable.  Built well, this 2600 Sqft house has a lot of space. It is zoned residential agricultural.  There are two boat landings close by on the Crooked River.  Highways 67 and 98 provide simple access to major urban areas.  The home is located 5 miles from the seaside town of Carrabelle, and 30 minutes from one of the most beautiful beaches in the US with its white sand beaches and warm waters.  The improved fiber optic upgrades in our area will provide additional internet possibilities..  Our property is adjacent to the National Forest which provides a greater feeling of natural space. Most of all the serenity and peacefulness makes this property amazing.
